parameters:
[Gisellemina] Is it already over? It wasn't as big of a deal as you
made it out to be~♪

[Gisellemina] I was thinking of corrupting you to the point where you
would willingly open your legs more, but how disappointing...

[Gisellemina] While you're still in a sane state of mind... I'll let
you experience the shame of a genius girl to the fullest ♥
[Anastasia] (M-My body... it's not moving as I want it to...)

[Gisellemina] (Your body isn't moving because I'm controlling it right
now♪)
[Anastasia] (What on earth... What do you intend to do...?!)
